name: Hexapuss
summary:
Hexapuss  
"The End Has Six Tentacles"

Enter the chaos! In Hexapuss, step into a mind-bending VR pinball machine where the stakes are as massive as Hexapuss itself. Take control, hit the ball, and try to confront the interdimensional six-tentacled menace. Will you save Hexapuss or destroy it? The power is in your hands. 

Key Features:  
First-Person Pinball**: Immerse yourself in the machine as you take aim and control the action like never before.
